GammaNuEta: Gamma Nu Eta was established as the National Information Technology Honor Society to recognize and promote leadership and excellence in the study of IT. We provide academic services such as tutoring and run career-related events such as the Company Expose.

Our President: Andrew Smith is a dual Computer Science and ITWS major of Class of 2022. He's also a freelance web developer at Smith Branch Rentals. Contact him at smitha24@rpi.edu.
